As Tonto Dikeh nurses the pains of her failed marriage which produced a child, that of her counterpart, Mercy Johnson has continued to flourish. Nollywood actress, Mercy Johnson, her husband, Prince Odi Okojie and their three kids are serving family goals in new photos she shared via her social media space. Her marriage has been working for some years now and she seems to be at peace with her family. She is one of the few actresses far away from scandals and social media controversies.